"0000║$m_z018fl_fg001" = "Guess it's time to 'face the peril of our plight.'{Text NewLine}Sounds splendid.{End}{Escape}Fang";
"0001║$m_z018fl_fg002" = "Try and keep calm. Don't want to go giving those brands any big ideas.{End}{Escape}Fang";
"0002║$m_z018fl_fg003" = "I don't like this place. The air's all gone to rot.{End}{Escape}Fang";
"0003║$m_z018fl_fg004" = "Huh. All this time, I thought these Arks were stories.{End}{Escape}Fang";
"0004║$m_z018fl_fg005" = "Seeing as we're here, I guess we might as well make use of the fal'Cie's complimentary training program.{End}{Escape}Fang";
"0005║$m_z018fl_fg006" = "These things are from Gran Pulse.{End}{Escape}Fang";
