"0008║$m_z018fl_ho001" = "This place is huge. I wonder how far it goes?{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0009║$m_z018fl_ho002" = "Do you suppose Orphan and Eden are waiting in here?{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0010║$m_z018fl_ho003" = "This whole place must have been brought here when Cocoon was being built.{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0011║$m_z018fl_ho004" = "He wants to make us stronger so we can destroy Cocoon.{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0012║$m_z018fl_ho005" = "I doubt the people in the Sanctum even know about this place.{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0013║$m_z018fl_ho006" = "If word got out about this place, Cocoon would go crazy.{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0014║$m_z018fl_lift" = "ACTIVATE{End}{Escape}";
"0015║$m_z018fl_lt001" = "I want to say we're close to Eden, but...it's hard to be sure.{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0016║$m_z018fl_lt002" = "The footing's a little iffy, but we should be able to get across.{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0017║$m_z018fl_lt003" = "Well, at least we shouldn't run into PSICOM here.{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0018║$m_z018fl_lt004" = "The Sanctum fal'Cie want to train Pulse l'Cie?{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0019║$m_z018fl_lt005" = "So all these were sealed in here? But why?{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0020║$m_z018fl_lt006" = "If all these things escaped...I don't even want to think about what would happen to Cocoon.{End}{Escape}Lightning";
"0021║$m_z018fl_sn001" = "So, we really are being trained to attack Cocoon.{End}{Escape}Snow";
"0022║$m_z018fl_sn002" = "Everything Pulse is an enemy of Cocoon.{End}{Escape}Snow";
"0023║$m_z018fl_sz001" = "The size of this place!{Text NewLine}How do you hide something like this?{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0024║$m_z018fl_sz002" = "What's this Dysley—or uh, Bart-an-dealio character trying to do, anyway?{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0025║$m_z018fl_sz003" = "This thing's old. Real old.{Text NewLine}Might even be older than Cocoon, come to think of it.{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0026║$m_z018fl_sz004" = "So this Ark thing's here to train us up for the end of the world, huh?{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0027║$m_z018fl_sz005" = "The armies of Pulse, all wrapped up in a nice little package?{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0028║$m_z018fl_sz006" = "If you're gonna Purge something, why don't you Purge this place?{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0029║$m_z018fl_talk" = "TALK{End}{Escape}";
"0030║$m_z018fl_va001" = "We try to go back to Gran Pulse, and we end up here.{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0031║$m_z018fl_va002" = "I don't know what's waiting for us here, but we'd better stick together.{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0032║$m_z018fl_va003" = "This couldn't be—I mean, those were just legends, right?{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0033║$m_z018fl_va004" = "What do you suppose happens to l'Cie when their full powers wake up?{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0034║$m_z018fl_va005" = "Whatever it is the fal'Cie want, we're the ones who decide what we do.{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0035║$m_z018fl_va006" = "We better leave those things alone. Wouldn't want them waking up.{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0036║$m_z018fl_va007" = "Why don't you just, uh, keep sleeping there? All right?{End}{Escape}Vanille";
"0037║$t_fark01_cap_01" = "Your party members have unlocked the potential to assume {Color Red}all combat roles{Color SkyBlue}!{Text NewLine}From now on, you may also {Color Red}freely select the members of your battle team{Color SkyBlue}.{Text NewLine}To take on a new role, a member must first learn an ability for that role.{Text NewLine}You can teach a party member new abilities via the {Color Gold}Crystarium{Color SkyBlue}.";
"0038║$zn018_000fa" = "Been checking your brand?";
"0039║$zn018_000ho" = "So Dysley was really the fal'Cie Barthandelus.";
"0040║$zn018_000ho_st" = "Are we ready to get out of here?{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0041║$zn018_000sn" = "Serah... So gathering up the tools for destruction{Text NewLine}turned you to crystal, huh?";
"0042║$zn018_000sz" = "Wish I could say it was my piloting skills that saved us{Text NewLine}back there, but it wasn't.";
"0043║$zn018_000va" = "Don't believe everything a fal'Cie says.";
"0044║$zn018_001fa" = "You start to stray, or take too much of a shock, your brand will change and it'll be 'Next stop: Cie'th Central.'";
"0045║$zn018_001ho" = "The vision he was talking about was that crazy Ragnarok dream we all had when we were made into l'Cie.";
"0046║$zn018_001sz" = "Truth is, the ship handled all the flying and shooting.";
"0047║$zn018_001va" = "He's telling us our Focus is to destroy Cocoon,{Text NewLine}but who knows?";
"0048║$zn018_002fa" = "Keep that in mind.";
"0049║$zn018_002ho" = "One of us is supposed to become this Ragnarok thing and destroy Eden.";
"0050║$zn018_002sz" = "And I'm not talking about some jacked-up autopilot, either.";
"0051║$zn018_002va" = "He could be lying to trick us into helping him{Text NewLine}to do something else.";
"0052║$zn018_003ho" = "Except we do that by destroying this 'Orphan' that gives Eden its power.";
"0053║$zn018_003sz" = "Something wanted us to make it out of there, and made sure we did.";
"0054║$zn018_003va" = "We should listen to Serah, not some fal'Cie.";
"0055║$zn018_004ho" = "I think I have that part straight now.";
"0056║$zn018_005ho_st" = "Continue into the ruins?{End}{Escape}";
"0057║$zn018_010fa" = "My brand's as messed up as the rest of me. Never changes.";
"0058║$zn018_010ho" = "So, Serah's real Focus was to gather a fresh batch of l'Cie candidates who could attack Cocoon.";
"0059║$zn018_010ho_st" = "Yeah, we'd better think this through.{End}{Escape}Hope";
"0060║$zn018_010sn" = "You really were an enemy of Cocoon.";
"0061║$zn018_010sn2" = "Just like the rest of us.{End}{Escape}Snow";
"0062║$zn018_010sz" = "Hey, uh...";
"0063║$zn018_010sz2" = "I don't know what's waiting for us out there, but we{Text NewLine}can't sit around here worrying about it.{End}{Escape}Sazh";
"0064║$zn018_010va" = "No matter what our Focus is, we still make our own decisions.";
"0065║$zn018_011fa" = "I might be able to get away with ignoring my Focus, but the rest of you ain't so lucky.";
"0066║$zn018_011ho" = "We all showed up at the Pulse fal'Cie's place, so she turned to crystal.";
"0067║$zn018_011sn" = "I had it all wrong. Totally wrong.";
"0068║$zn018_011sz" = "We've got to suck it up and face reality here.";
"0069║$zn018_011va" = "Worse comes to worst, we can always just do nothing and wait for time to run out.";
"0070║$zn018_012fa" = "I don't even want to think about being the only one left, herding a flock of Cie'th around.";
"0071║$zn018_012ho" = "Snow was wrong from the start, then.{Text NewLine}We were never supposed to save Cocoon.";
"0072║$zn018_012sz" = "Snow's falling apart. So it's up to you and me to keep{Text NewLine}things steady.";
"0073║$zn018_012va" = "After all, there's no stopping our brands.";
"0074║$zn018_013ho" = "That makes a lot more sense. Not that I'm happy about it.";
"0075║$zn018_020fa" = "Snow's taking this all pretty hard.";
"0076║$zn018_020ho" = "Raines should be off fighting the Sanctum by now.";
"0077║$zn018_020ho_st" = "";
"0078║$zn018_020sn" = "I only made it this far because I thought we were{Text NewLine}the world's last hope.";
"0079║$zn018_020sz" = "Vanille told me everything.";
"0080║$zn018_020va" = "I got on that Purge train on my own.";
"0081║$zn018_021fa" = "Seeing him go from being so damn upbeat to such a mopey wreck is making {Italic}me{Italic} feel depressed.";
"0082║$zn018_021ho" = "We've got to get out of here and join up with him.";
"0083║$zn018_021sz" = "Told me who else was responsible for Euride Gorge.";
"0084║$zn018_021va" = "The Sanctum said we'd just be shipped out of Cocoon,{Text NewLine}and I believed it.";
"0085║$zn018_022fa" = "I'm worried about his brand.";
"0086║$zn018_022ho" = "But still—rushing straight into the middle of the fight is probably just what Dysley wants us to do.";
"0087║$zn018_022sz" = "Ah, never mind. Now's not the time.";
"0088║$zn018_022va" = "I thought if I went back to Gran Pulse with that fal'Cie,{Text NewLine}I might be able to escape all this.";
"0089║$zn018_023va" = "But I guess things have a funny way of catching up with you.";
"0090║$zn018_030sn" = "Now, it's destroy Cocoon or become a Cie'th?";
"0091║$zn018_031sn" = "Damn it!";
